<p><strong>Fees:</strong> CHF. 5.- per item. Fee is paid cash at pickup. Items not picked up will still be charged CHF 5.-.</p>
<p><strong>Delivery times:</strong> Items ordered online are picked-up daily via IDS delivery service (except on Saturdays) and normally delivered within two working days to the pick-up library of your choice. They can be picked up within one week of delivery.</p>

