<p>The internal delivery service in <a href="http://www.unibe.ch/universitaet/dienstleistungen/universitaetsbibliothek/service/ausleihe/kurier/index_ger.html" target="_blank">Bern</a> is free. Please check our <a href="http://www.unibe.ch/university/services/university_library/services/borrowing/courier/delivery_times_bernese_courier/index_eng.html" target="_blank">website</a> for delivery times.</p>

